                    Brand</th>
                  <th
                    class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-white uppercase tracking-wider whitespace-nowrap">
                    Model</th>
                  <th
                    class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-white uppercase tracking-wider whitespace-nowrap">
                    Date of Purchase</th>
                  <th
                    class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-white uppercase tracking-wider whitespace-nowrap">
                    Date of Entry</th>
                  <th
                    class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-white uppercase tracking-wider whitespace-nowrap">
                    User</th>
                  <th
                    class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-white uppercase tracking-wider whitespace-nowrap">
                    Department</th>
                  <th
                    class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-white uppercase tracking-wider whitespace-nowrap">
                    Type of Peripheral</th>
                  <th
                    class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-white uppercase tracking-wider whitespace-nowrap">
                    Serial No.</th>
                  <th
                    class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-white uppercase tracking-wider whitespace-nowrap">
                    Property Tag</th>
                  <th
                    class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-white uppercase tracking-wider whitespace-nowrap">
                    Peripheral No.</th>
                  <th
                    class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-white uppercase tracking-wider whitespace-nowrap">
                    Peripheral Status</th>
                  <th
